          "reviewBody": "The school offers numerous opportunities for students to pursue their sports passion and lead active lifestyles. Experienced coaches guide DPS students to excel in their chosen sports and learn invaluable lessons in teamwork, discipline, and sportsmanship. It combines traditional teaching methods with an experimental learning methodology that fosters curiosity, creativity, and critical thinking skills through hands-on activities. Integrating activities into the curriculum allows students to explore concepts firsthand and make meaningful connections between theory and practice.DPS emphasizes the importance of experiential learning through a variety of hands-on activities that extend beyond the classroom.",
