            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am blessed to be a part of DPS 67 A  Gurugram.  I strongly recommend it to everyone looking for holistic development of their child . The facilities at the school are top-notch, providing students with a safe and inspiring space to explore and grow. From well-equipped classrooms to modern technology resources, the school is clearly invested in creating an optimal learning environment. The extracurricular activities and clubs offered provide additional opportunities for students to discover and nurture their interests.",
          "publisher": {
