          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's an incredible school! The pedagogical learning approach they follow really helps students understand concepts deeply. They also provide plenty of hands-on experiences, which make learning more engaging and practical. The emphasis on experiential learning allows students to apply their knowledge in real-life situations. Overall, DPS is a fantastic school that nurtures holistic development and prepares students for the future. I highly recommend it! 😄👍",
          "publisher": {
