            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The DPS Sec-67 A is a well-established and reputable institution that offers a comprehensive education for students. The school has a strong academic curriculum with a focus on both traditional subjects and modern technology. The faculty is highly qualified and dedicated to the success of their students.\n\nThe school also places a strong emphasis on extracurricular activities, providing students with opportunities to explore their interests and talents outside of the classroom. The facilities are also top-notch, with well-equipped classrooms, laboratories, and sports facilities.\n\nThe school has a strong sense of community and provides a supportive and nurturing environment for students to learn and grow. The management and staff are committed to the overall development of the students and work tirelessly to ensure their success.\n\nOverall, DPS Sec-67 is a fantastic school that provides a well-rounded education for its students. It is definitely worth considering for parents looking for a quality educational institution for their children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
